      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BENTLEY OLAF (6) shapes nicely here coming off a brilliant 19.65 victory at Capalaba over 366m. Has the ability and looks hard to top. OUTPLAYED (8) is an honest type rarely out of the money, scoring at this track (25.37) last time and making it two straight wins. Form here sound including six wins. Expected to feature on best form. SUNSET DREAMING (1) is a talented type and proved too classy last time to win by 2 lengths at this track in a handy 19.99 beating Billy Balowski. Safe beginner who draws ideally on the inside. Can make it back-to-back wins. CANYA ATOMIC (2) must be respected despite an unplaced effort here most recently.",
